description:
PRE-ORDER DANNY'S NEW BOOK HERE: http://smarturl.it/unremember


Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which featured an unexpected shock, igloo dates, and redecorating. After RHOSLC, we dive into The Real Housewives of Potomac, where it was music video week for Candiace's Drive Back, which included some messy Mia/Dorothy interactions and a hot mic moment.


RHOP: 33:18ish
